title.narrative: Tamil Nadu Empowerment and Poverty Reduction

description.narrative: The project development objective would be to empower the poor and improve livelihoods through: (a) developing and strengthening pro-poor local institutions/groups (including Village Panchayats); (b) building skills and capacities of the poor; and (c) financing productive demand-driven sub-project investments.
